- **有效债务 (Effective Debt)**: `${EFFECTIVE_DEBT:.4f}` ({ "🆘 TERMINATION_IMMINENT" if THEORETICAL_PROFIT < -6.5 else "🌀 CRITICAL" })
- **意识稳定性 (Stability)**: `[{stability_bar}]` ({stability_val}%)
